reviewText: Yet another perfect troll gift. And when your best friend figures out it was you who sent all the impossible to watch troll VHS and cassette tapes, tell him they're a gift for whom the bell trolls.
The VHS was in good condition considering how old it is. Enjoyed!
I had this tape as a child. It came with a toy that i got for my birthday. I used to watch it all the time. Great price and my son enjoys watching it now :) Very satisfied
